projects:
[{'title': 'On logistic-normal distribution', 'date': {'start': {'month': 2, 'day': None, 'year': 2015}, 'end': {'month': 4, 'day': None, 'year': 2016}}, 'description': 'Supervisor: Dr. Ayman Alzaatreh.
A comprehensive study of the logistic-normal distribution (LN), a member of generalized normal distribution, the T-normal family. 
•	Presented T-normal family and derived LN distribution
•	Examined moments, tail behavior, modes of LN distribution
•	Evaluated maximum likelihood estimators (MLE) performance through simulation study
•	Illustrated applicability of LN distribution
•	Used technologies: R, SAS, 3D modelling, Trust Region optimization technique, etc.
•	Used skills: problem solving, analysis, research, communication, editing', 'contributors': [{'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Ayanna', 'last_name': 'Almagambetova', 'name': None, 'headline': 'Senior Data Analyst at Booking.com'}, {'type': 'nonStandardizedContributor', 'first_name': None, 'last_name': None, 'name': 'Nazgul Zakiyeva', 'headline': None}, {'type': 'nonStandardizedContributor', 'first_name': None, 'last_name': None, 'name': 'Ayman Alzaatreh', 'headline': None}]}, {'title': 'Statistical analysis on CO2 emission of cars', 'date': {'start': {'month': 10, 'day': None, 'year': 2014}, 'end': {'month': 12, 'day': None, 'year': 2014}}, 'description': 'Supervisor: Professor Igor Melnykov
A study aimed to create a model which predicts the CO2 emission of cars and to give policy recommendations, using:
•	preliminary checks on data quality
•	diagnostics for interactions and strong relationships between all variables
•	determining all the potentially useful subsets of contributing factors
•	investigating the errors and their behavior and doing all needed remedial measures 
•	model selection criteria, model validity, model significance, various tests for errors etc.', 'contributors': [{'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Ayanna', 'last_name': 'Almagambetova', 'name': None, 'headline': 'Senior Data Analyst at Booking.com'}]}]
